            (fill col)            
            (rect 25 25 50 50))
          
          (define (on-mouse-pressed)
            (:= col (- 255 col)))]


@bold{Usage}

@racketusage[(define (on-mouse-pressed) <body>)]        @linebreak[]


@bold{Description}


If defined in your program, the event handler @racket[on-mouse-pressed]
